NamingString.DescriptorBrandedFeatureString: electric razor with Flex & Pivot Action

Product.SubWOW: Perfectly close, even on the neck
Product.MarketingTextHeader: For men who only want the very best, arcitec combines Flex & Pivot Action with the Triple-Track shaving heads for a perfectly close shave, even on the neck

KeyBenefitArea.KeyBenefitAreaName: Perfectly close, even on the neck

Feature.FeatureGlossary: Three independently flexing heads in a shaving unit that swivels with a full range of motion. This unique combination ensures optimum skin contact in curved areas to catch even the most problematic neck hair.

KeyBenefitArea.KeyBenefitAreaName: For a faster and closer shave

Feature.FeatureGlossary: The three shaving tracks of the Triple Track shaving heads offer 50% more shaving surface than standard, single track rotary shaving heads.
Ultra thin heads with slots to shave long hairs and unique micro holes designed to catch the shortest stubble.
Dual blade system: first blade lifts, second blade cuts for a comfortable close shave.
The waterproof shaver can be easily rinsed under the tap.
Patented tube trimmer technology for great precision and maneuverability. Perfect for contouring and trimming moustache and sideburns.
